@url = http://127.0.0.1:3000

### Chequear Express
GET {{url}}/health

### Chequear Base de Datos
GET {{url}}/health/db

### ==============================
### CRUD DE USUARIOS
### ==============================

### 1. CREAR UN USUARIO (STUDENT)
POST {{url}}/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Nicolás Badenes",
  "email": "nicolasbadenes@epet12smandes.edu.ar",
  "password_hash": "supersecreta123",
  "role": "STUDENT"
}

### 2. CREAR UN PROFESOR (Para probar la relación con materias)
POST {{url}}/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Profesor de Programación",
  "email": "profe@epet12smandes.edu.ar",
  "password_hash": "supersecreta123",
  "role": "PROFESSOR"
}

### 3. OBTENER TODOS LOS USUARIOS (GET)
GET {{url}}/users

### 4. OBTENER UN USUARIO POR ID (GET)
GET {{url}}/users/1

### 5. ACTUALIZAR UN USUARIO (PUT)
PUT {{url}}/users/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Nicolás B.",
  "role": "STUDENT"
}

### 6. ELIMINAR UN USUARIO (DELETE)
DELETE {{url}}/users/3


### ==============================
### CRUD DE MATERIAS (SUBJECTS)
### ==============================

### 1. CREAR UNA MATERIA
POST {{url}}/materias
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Construcción de Software",
  "description": "Trabajo práctico integrador",
  "professor_id": 2
}

### 2. OBTENER TODAS LAS MATERIAS
GET {{url}}/materias

### 3. OBTENER MATERIA POR ID
GET {{url}}/materias/1

### 4. ACTUALIZAR UNA MATERIA
PUT {{url}}/materias/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Análisis Matemático",
  "description": "Nueva descripción actualizada"
}

### 5. ELIMINAR UNA MATERIA
DELETE {{url}}/materias/1


### ==============================
### INSCRIPCIONES (ENROLLMENTS)
### ==============================

### 1. INSCRIBIR ALUMNO A MATERIA
POST {{url}}/relaciones/cursa
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "student_id": 1,
  "subject_id": 1
}

### 2. PROBAR RESTRICCIÓN DE INSCRIPCIÓN (OPCIONAL)
POST {{url}}/relaciones/cursa
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "student_id": 1,
  "subject_id": 1
}